%CO:A,12,72%Garden Improvements

To: Browns Garden Maintenance

We would like to carry out the following work in our garden 
during the Autumn. 

Please could you send a quotation for the work and let us
know if any of it should take place at a different time of
year.

1. Front garden: : Level out raised bed. Prepare soil and 
plant with heathers, bedding plants and evergreen shrubs.  
2. Back garden: Plant spring bulbs along bottom hedge.

3. Greenhouse: Repair broken catch on door.

4. Side wall: Erect a trellis against the wall and plant a 
virginia creeper at its base.

Please let us know when you would be able to carry out
the work.
